  "local_port": 35234,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some cool Pok\u00e9mon GO gadgets to buy?",
  "response": "Pok\u00e9mon GO has inspired a variety of gadgets and accessories to enhance gameplay, track stats, and make the experience more fun. Here are some cool Pok\u00e9mon GO gadgets to consider:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Pok\u00e9mon GO Plus +**\n   - **What it does**: A wrist-worn device that connects to your phone via Bluetooth. It notifies you of nearby Pok\u00e9mon and Pok\u00e9Stops, allowing you to catch Pok\u00e9mon or collect items with a button press without looking at your phone.\n   - **Why it's cool**: It\u2019s an upgraded version of the original Pok\u00e9mon GO Plus, with additional features like tracking sleep for Pok\u00e9mon Sleep integration.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Gotcha Evolve**\n   - **What it does**: A wearable device that automatically spins Pok\u00e9Stops and catches Pok\u00e9mon without pressing a button.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Its hands-free automation makes it perfect for players who want to focus on walking or other activities while playing.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Pok\u00e9mon GO Auto Catch/Wristband Devices**\n   - **What it does**: Similar to Gotcha Evolve, these devices automatically catch Pok\u00e9mon and spin Pok\u00e9Stops.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Affordable alternatives to branded gadgets, often with customizable settings for catching and spinning.\n\n---\n\n### **4. Portable Phone Charger (Power Bank)**\n   - **What it does**: Keeps your phone charged during long Pok\u00e9mon GO sessions.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Essential for extended gameplay, especially during community days or raids.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Pok\u00e9mon GO AR Glasses (or AR Headsets)**\n   - **What it does**: Enhances the Augmented Reality (AR) experience by overlaying Pok\u00e9mon onto the real world through glasses or headsets.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Takes immersion to the next level, making it feel like Pok\u00e9mon are truly in your environment.\n\n---\n\n### **6. Pok\u00e9mon GO Backpack or Bag**\n   - **What it does**: A stylish backpack designed for carrying Pok\u00e9mon GO essentials like water, snacks, and power banks.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Combines functionality with fandom, often featuring Pok\u00e9mon designs.\n\n---\n\n### **7. Pok\u00e9mon GO Egg Incubator Tracker**\n   - **What it does**: A physical device or app that tracks the distance you\u2019ve walked for egg hatching.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Helps you stay on top of your egg-hatching progress without constantly checking your phone.\n\n---\n\n### **8. Pok\u00e9mon GO Gamepad**\n   - **What it does**: A Bluetooth gamepad designed for easier control in Pok\u00e9mon GO.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Adds a console-like experience to the game, especially useful for battling and catching.\n\n---\n\n### **9. Pok\u00e9mon GO Adventure Sync Pedometer**\n   - **What it does**: Tracks your steps even when the app is closed, syncing with the game to count distance for eggs and buddy candy.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Lets you play passively while still making progress.\n\n---\n\n### **10. Pok\u00e9mon GO Cooling Phone Case**\n   - **What it does**: Prevents your phone from overheating during long gameplay sessions.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Keeps your phone running smoothly, even in hot weather.\n\n---\n\n### **11. Pok\u00e9mon GO Raid Pass Holder**\n   - **What it does**: A physical holder for your raid passes, often designed like a Pok\u00e9 Ball.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Keeps your passes organized and adds to the Pok\u00e9mon theme.\n\n---\n\n### **12. Pok\u00e9mon GO Luggage Tag or Keychain**\n   - **What it does**: A decorative accessory featuring Pok\u00e9mon GO designs.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Perfect for showing off your passion for the game in everyday life.\n\n---\n\n### **13. Pok\u00e9mon GO Training Mat**\n   - **What it does**: A mat with resistance bands and exercises designed to encourage movement while playing.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Combines fitness with gameplay, making it a fun way to stay active.\n\n---\n\n### **14. Pok\u00e9mon GO Smartwatch Apps**\n   - **What it does**: Apps for smartwatches like Apple Watch or Garmin that track your progress, notify you of nearby Pok\u00e9mon, and more.\n   - **Why it's cool**: Integrates seamlessly with your wearable tech for a streamlined experience.\n\n---\n\nThese gadgets can enhance your Pok\u00e9mon GO experience, whether you're a casual player or a dedicated Trainer. Always check compatibility with your device before purchasing!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
